### 触发激励任务：每日登录
POST http://localhost:8080/app/task/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "eventCode": "daily_login",
  "eventRuleData": {
    "value": true
  },
  "source": "user",
  "uniqueSourceId": {{$timestamp}}
}

